<main class="container mt-5">
    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p>This website is an integration of the NASA Astronomy Picture of the Day (APOD) API using Express.js and Axios. The goal of this project is to provide users with the astronomy picture of the day and its information, showcasing the capabilities of API integration and server-side programming.</p>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Displays NASA's Astronomy Picture of the Day</li>
        <li>Uses Express.js for server-side routing</li>
        <li>Fetches data from NASA's public API using Axios</li>
        <li>Responsive design using Bootstrap</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Technologies Used</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Node.js</li>
        <li>Express.js</li>
        <li>Axios</li>
        <li>EJS (Embedded JavaScript) for templating</li>
        <li>Bootstrap for styling</li>
        <li>dotenv for environment variable management</li>
    </ul>

</main>
